            <scopecontent id="aspace_513b554083d061cfd9c6ea0167b34767">
               <head>Scope and Contents</head>
               <p>The series contains autograph manuscripts by Audubon composed for his publications relating to birds and quadrupeds. Interfiled with Audubon's own writings for his <title localtype="simple" render="italic">
                     <part>Ornithological Biography</part>
                  </title> are several autograph manuscript entries by naturalists Thomas McCulloch (1776-1843), Thomas Nuttall (1786-1859), and John Kirk Townsend (1809-1851).</p>
            </scopecontent>
